About Game:
************
The bestselling Dark Parable series continues with The Little Mermaid and the Purple Tide! Follow the clues as they take you to an underwater kingdom in this exciting hidden-object puzzle adventure game!
You've been called to investigate a strange purple tide. And that's when the mermaid shows up... 

Once again, as the famous detective with an immense background in solving the fairy tale related cases, you are sent to arrive on the sun-bathed coast of Crete. As you sail on, your briefing is cut short when the monstrous eel rises from the sea and breaks your boat apart.

Stranded on the nearby coast, you come face to face with the mermaid who warns you to leave, but before you know it, accompanied by the mysterious stranger, you enter the temple that had risen out of the water and uncover it leads to the legendary underwater kingdom of Prasino.

As the secrets of the sunken kingdom begin to unravel, your investigation turns into a race with time to stop the ancient power from releasing its rage upon the world. Can you find a way to rid the kingdom of the unearthly shadows from the deep and endure the whelm of the purple tide? 

Game Features:
**************
A variety of hidden-object scenes, including fractured objects!
The bonus game unlocks the secrets of Prasino's mad king
Achievements
Available Strategy Guide
Wallpapers and concept art


